[background arg="res://assets/temp/tempCafe/Cafe_Interior.jpg" fade="1.5"]
if {Drink.Rating} == "none":
	jump begin_timeline
else:
	jump drink_rating
label begin_timeline
audio music "res://assets/audio/cafe_bgm.ogg" [fade="2.0" volume="-8.0"]
# DAY #, SCENE #
join  center
Player: [i]A cat's coming to the counter. I don't think I've seen this one before.[/i]
What a simply marvelous place you have here. So wonderous. So perfect in its imperfect way.
[signal arg="drink_hint"]
**DRINK HINT HERE**
leave 
[signal arg="craft_drink"]
label drink_rating (Scene 2 Drink Rating)
[background arg="res://assets/temp/tempCafe/Cafe_Interior.jpg" fade="1.5" wait="true"]
audio music "res://assets/audio/craft_drink_bgm.ogg" [fade="2.0" volume="-5.0"]
if {Drink.Rating} == "mediocre":
	join  center
	That was quite a nice little drink. Thank you for your service to my needs.
	leave 
	[signal arg="clear_drink"]
elif {Drink.Rating} == "good":
	join  center
	Now that was just pure perfection. No more. No Less.
	leave 
	[signal arg="clear_drink"]
else:
	# Bad
	join  center
	What a most interesting mystery. You seem to have made a truly undrinkable concoction. Let's see if you can attempt this endeavor again.
	leave 
	[signal arg="clear_drink"]
	[signal arg="craft_drink"]
Player: [i]What a strange cat. And what was all that he was going on about?[/i]
[signal arg="end_encounter"]
[end_timeline]